    <dlgPart>
      <portrait />
      <speaker_name>Centurion</speaker_name>
      <npc_text>The Centurion assigns you to a five-man unit, led by a Decanus – a legionary in charge of a small unit. From what you've heard Decanii usually commanded ten-man units, but things are different today.

"Alright, boys. You heard the Commander. We're taking over, one tower at a time." He grins. "Once we control the perimeter – the gate and the towers – Teron is ours. House Daratan will be under siege and cut off. I'll be surprised if they last a week.

"Now, your task is to capture this tower." He marks it on his map. "Inform the local guards that their services are no longer required. If they resist, kill them. Dismissed."</npc_text>
